Set up a table as follows below:
K Q J 10 9 8
             7
A 2 3 4 5 6

Dealer flips the top card of the deck, showing it to the players
Players then place bets on cards on the table

Dealer flips 2 cards
    First card is the loser. All bets placed on it are lost
    Second card is the winner. All bets pay out 1:1
    Rest of the bets stay on the table
Players then place new bets
Repeat until 3 cards are left

Players then guess the order of the final 3 cards
    payout is 4:1